transcript.text: Welcome to Entrend shop.
Today we will see how to assign product to a corporate, add corporate price to a product and assign templates to a particular corporate.
So first of all for adding a product or assigning a product to a particular corporate, go to products, then select the particular product and then click on action button and then edit button.
Over here, on the right hand side, you'll have an option to select user type.
In this user type, you can select the specific corporate.
From here, just click on this drop down, select the specific corporate.
You can assign to a single corporate or multiple corporates from here.
And also you can assign this particular product to all corporates from here.
So from here you can assign the product to a corporate.
Even when you are adding a product, you click on add button and you have an option over here to select user type where you can select all corporate or specific corporate.
You can select from here.
So this is how you can assign a product to the corporate.
And when you go into the corporate over here under assign products, you can see the products assigned to all corporate or product assigned to a specific corporate.
So this is how you can assign a product to the corporate.
Now adding the product price to a particular corporate, for that under products you go to this price tab, select from here common price or corporate or a single corporate or specific corporate.
Then for that specific corporate or for all corporate you can add quantity and price over here and click on save button.
So this is how you can add particular prices for particular corporate or all corporate in the product.
So this we have seen how to add product and how to add prices to a particular corporate.
Now we'll see how to assign a template to a particular corporate.
So for that you go to the template sections product templates.
Then click on action button, click on edit info.
Now after that you can select the user type.

From here in the user type, you can select either all corporates or you can select a particular corporate and for particular corporate you can even select a particular department for which you want to assign the template.
And then after selecting this you can complete the rest of the details over here and then click on 7 continue or 7 back.
Even when you are adding a template at that point when you click on add button while adding the new template, you have option to select user type over here.
And from here you can select all corporates or a particular corporate and for particular corporate you can select all department or a particular department for this particular template.
So this is how you can assign a product to the corporate.
You can assign a template to a corporate and you can add product prices for particular corporate or all the corporates.
Thank you for watching this video.
